Bootstrap Directory Structure

1. CSS Folder
Contains Bootstrap CSS files.
Used for styling web pages, buttons, forms, layouts, colors, typography and responsive design.

2. JS Folder
Contains Bootstrap JavaScript files.
Used for interactive components such as modals, dropdowns, accordions, carousels and tooltips.

3. Icons Folder
Contains Bootstrap Icons.
Used to add graphical icons such as home, search, user and social media icons to web pages.